4088     // While we theoretically can erase EH, that would result in a block that
4089     // used to start with an EH no longer starting with EH, which is invalid.
4090     // To make it valid, we'd need to fixup predecessors to no longer refer to
4091     // this block, but that changes CFG, which is not allowed in InstCombine.
